    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and practicality. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, showing only minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple with minimal bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side, and all electronic features\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and navigation\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. It recently underwent a full inspection, receiving fresh fluids and new brake pads, while the tires show plenty of remaining tread. While it shows the light character of a well-loved car, it has been kept to a high standard, making it a reliable and sophisticated choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
