    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super dependable, and it still runs like a dream! It\u2019s the perfect companion for daily commutes or weekend adventures, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep it clean and ready for its next owner. I\u2019d love for this to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
