    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The powertrain benefits from a recent VANOS service and valve adjustment, ensuring optimal cam timing and throttle response across the 8,000 RPM sweep. The chassis is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential and remains structurally sound with a reinforced subframe. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak lateral grip and linear power delivery. A visceral, naturally aspirated machine for the purist who values mechanical pedigree and tactile feedback.",
